\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Wardrobe planning - Principles and steps involved in wardrobe planning, Points to be considered while planning wardrobe for different age groups.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7044693 U}{\b\insrsid7044693 nit}{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7044693 -III\tab (20 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Apparel Designing- Body measurements, Importance of body measurements in garment construction. Preparation of pattern, Drafting, principles of Drafting, Draping and commercial patterns, Layout planning-types of lay out. Merits and Demerits.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7044693 U}{\b\insrsid7044693 nit}{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7044693 - IV\tab (20 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Laundry- Method of washing. Water, Detergents and soap less detergents, soap, and soap manufacture. Review of laundry materials. Laundering and finishing of different fabrics with special refer to cotton, silk and wool.
\par }{\insrsid7044693 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7044693 U}{\b\insrsid7044693 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7044693 -V\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Designs- Traditional textiles and embroidery of India (Understanding the concepts only). Care and maintenance- Stain removal-Types of stains, Principles and Techniques of removal.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7044693 RELATED EXPERIENCES
