\par CORE }{\b\insrsid1665940\charrsid7741991 COURSE V}{\b\insrsid8140990 I}{\b\insrsid1665940\charrsid7741991  \endash  }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid1665940 COMMUNITY NUTRITION
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid3866909 {\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 {\*\bkmkstart page17}{\*\bkmkend page17}
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 OBJECTIVES
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par To understand the basic concepts of nutrition 
\par To understand the nutritional problems of community 
\par To know the ongoing intervention programmes to overcome malnutrition in the community 
\par To acquire skills in conducting nutrition education. 
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 U}{\b\insrsid9337186 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 - I\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid10177406 
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 Concepts of Nutrition-Definition of nutrition and health and their interrelationship. Balanced diet, basic principles of meals planning. ICMR recommended Dietary Allowances for all age groups.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 U}{\b\insrsid9337186 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 - II\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Assessment of Nutritional Status-Anthropometric, clinical, Biochemical and Dietary methods. Standards of nutritional status assessment and interpretation.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 U}{\b\insrsid9337186 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 - III\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Nutritional problems in the community-Importance of good nutrition, prevalence, etiology and measures to overcome malnutrition deficiency disorders \endash  PEM, micro nutrient deficiencies (Vitamin A, Vitam
in D Nutritional anemia, IDD, Zinc) Nutrition (obesity) \endash  Prevalence. Causes, Complications and dietary guidelines.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 U}{\b\insrsid9337186 nit}{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 -IV\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par National Nutrition programs- National nutrition policy, intervention programmes to combat malnutrition, mid day meal Programmer. Role of International organizations \endash  UNICEF, FAO, WHO
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 U}{\b\insrsid9337186 nit}{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid10177406 - V\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Nutrition Education-Definition, need, principles and methods of nutrition education.
\par \sect }\sectd \linex0\colno1\colw9360\sectdefaultcl\sectrsid3866909\sftnbj \pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid3866909 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
