\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par To impart basic and applied technology of baking and confectionary and acquaint with the manufacturing technology of bakery and confectionary products. 
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 U}{\b\insrsid12734796 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 \endash I\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Bakery and confectionary industry; raw materials and quality parameters; dough development; methods of dough mixing; dough chemistry; rheological testing of dough \endash 
 Farinograph, Mixograph, Extensograph, Amylograph/ Rapid Visco Analyzer, Falling number,}{\insrsid9709601  }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 Hosney\rquote s dough stickiness tester and interpretation of the data.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 U}{\b\insrsid12734796 nit}{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 - II\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Technology for the manufacture of bakery products \endash 
 bread, biscuits, cakes and the effect of variations in formulation and process parameters on the quality of the finished product; quality consideration and parameters; Staling and losses in baking; machineries used in bakery industry.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 U}{\b\insrsid12734796 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 - III\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Quality characteristics of confectionary ingredients; technology for manufacture of flour, fruit, milk, sugar, chocolate, and special confectionary products; colour, flavor and texture of confectiona
ry; standards and regulations; machineries used in confectionary industry.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 U}{\b\insrsid12734796 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 - IV\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Manufacture of bread rolls, sweet yeast dough products, cake specialties, pies and pastries, doughnuts, chocolates and candies; Maintenance, safety and hygiene of bakery plants.
\par }{\insrsid9709601 {\*\bkmkstart page36}{\*\bkmkend page36}
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 U}{\b\insrsid12734796 nit }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 \endash V\tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid9709601 
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 Testing of flour; Manufacture of bread, cake and biscuits; Analysis of bakery products; Cake icing techniques, water manufacture, cookies and crackers.
\par 
\par }{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 P}{\b\insrsid12734796 racticals}{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid9709601 \tab (15 Hours)
\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Determination of dough relaxation constants and their interpretation ; Development and quality evaluation of baked products based on composite flour; Preparation and quality evaluation of cakes, doughnuts, and pizza base; 
Effect of syrup consistency and temperature on the quality characteristics of hardboiled sweets; Preparation and quality evaluation of chocolate; Visit to bakery and Confectionery industries.
\par }{\b\insrsid12936460\charrsid7888798 Reference:}{\b\insrsid6777019\charrsid7888798 
