\par }{\insrsid6777019\charrsid3866909 
\par Guidance and Counseling \endash  Meaning, Nature, Scope, Principles, Goals, Needs of Guidance and Counseling of different groups, Relationship between guidance and counseling.
\par 
\par Types and Techniques used in guidance \endash  Educational, Vocational, Socio-personal, Leisure time guidance; Individual and Group Guidance \endash  Meaning and needs, Advantages, Techniques used; Role of audio-visual aids in guidance.
\par 
